Subject: [PATCH] -adding new native species 'Nightsiders', see also
 https://www.freeorion.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=7&t=11479 - they have
 Sanguine Sensorium sense to detect organic neighbours - likes and dislikes
 with motivational comments in the species definition file and translated into
 user friendly pedia page text - grooming typos crossing the t's and dotting
 the i's - moving the effect 'Light Sensitive' from banforo species definition
 to common population macros because the nightsiders share that trait - adding
 new species #2 the 'Sleepers', see also
 https://www.freeorion.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=7&t=12241 - add logging when
 preferred native focus not available during universe creation - change
 condition for availability of FOCUS_PROTECTION so that some native species
 with that same preferred focus can now do that while not yet conquored -
 adding new species #3 the khakturian. see also
 https://www.freeorion.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=7&t=12242

